{"tid":390473,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"教 局 副 局 長 蔡 若 蓮 兒 子 墮 樓 亡 (2)","createTime":"2017-09-07T06:16:39.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-07T06:24:12.000Z","uid":23707,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d44b1bbb4fb6984e9dacc0a2692da31d7bbbbbc7","tid":390473,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T06:16:39.000Z","msg":"Post 1<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/390386/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/390386/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170907/bkn-20170907121455773-0907_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170907%2Fbkn-20170907121455773-0907_00822_001.html&d=9KuE1y%2Fp8HLmKs9zaf6rKrIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=cc196c24\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170907/bkn-20170907121455773-0907_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n尖沙咀柯士甸道擎天半島發生墮樓案，早上11時許，大廈保安員突聞巨響，發現一名20餘歲男子倒臥在第3座平台對開，一臉鮮血陷入昏迷，於是報警。救護員及消防員到場，為傷者急救後送院，惜告死亡。警方初步相信男子由40多層高墮下，正調查其墮樓原因。<br />\n<br />\n現場消息稱，墮樓男子為教育局副局長蔡若蓮的兒子，蔡之前曾任教聯會副主席。"},{"pid":"c650679ceaaf667cef4e7b9696f7d72893f03713","tid":390473,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T06:18:31.000Z","msg":"Post 2<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/390466/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/390466/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"9ac4cd019ab354b521dd3aa7b49e4c5a7039c945","tid":390473,"uid":23170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T06:24:12.000Z","msg":"一個鐘就推爆，繼續慶祝啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 再正評先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}